{"tid":1032494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 泛民女社區主任報警　稱落區遭摸腳非禮","createTime":"2019-02-22T11:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T04:34:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9b91371877db2750d52bce07d1bf6b7ada5af837","tid":1032494,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"地區政團又爆出「MeToo」醜聞。將軍澳民生關注組昨晚（21日）於Facebook發表聲明，指其厚德社區主任王卓雅於街站工作期間被非禮，已報警求助。<br />\n王卓雅接受《香港01》訪問憶述事件經過，指有人趁她與街坊傾談期間，靠近她蹲下綁鞋帶並觸摸其腿部，隨後逃去，她認為不能啞忍，又感慨女性做地區工作，有時比男性受到更多制肘：「女仔落區困難會較多」。<br />\n曾任九龍城區議員多年的民主黨莫嘉嫻直言，做地區工作「間唔中都有遇過」類似事件，有長者會「恃老賣老」，向女性地區主任作出越界行為，她經常提醒同事出席公開活動時要保持警覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2471963/org/ffd5977c1cefd6c1b5b888fabed3952f.jpg/sS4KSolkwOBQN0qfaZg4YWcv5Sf-RJaBmt_48Zrf-PE?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2471963%2Forg%2Fffd5977c1cefd6c1b5b888fabed3952f.jpg%2FsS4KSolkwOBQN0qfaZg4YWcv5Sf-RJaBmt_48Zrf-PE%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=4f1107d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/298274/政壇metoo-泛民女社區主任報警-稱落區遭非禮-女仔落區唔易\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F298274%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87metoo-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6-%E7%A8%B1%E8%90%BD%E5%8D%80%E9%81%AD%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BB%94%E8%90%BD%E5%8D%80%E5%94%94%E6%98%93&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=55b113fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/298274/政壇metoo-泛民女社區主任報警-稱落區遭非禮-女仔落區唔易</a>"},{"pid":"856f727ad4fb36aecfef53508bcf6147e31a500e","tid":1032494,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2471575/org/92513f4aa468c2348f8fee9eb4065afc.jpg/97fg-K-YCYd73QeS6gPzIvbNYcWHTX9e1kA3zdZAN80?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2471575%2Forg%2F92513f4aa468c2348f8fee9eb4065afc.jpg%2F97fg-K-YCYd73QeS6gPzIvbNYcWHTX9e1kA3zdZAN80%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2ae40475&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c8f5f859c9ab92a6bd22013b5a4567971e6e3d1","tid":1032494,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74ccf39188d27225788a0cf87664525ed595d59","tid":1032494,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"期間有人趁她與街坊就社區議題傾談時，靠近她蹲下綁鞋帶，然後觸摸其腿部，隨後逃去。"},{"pid":"e08195603577355af5176a95318ff29fe418c004","tid":1032494,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:01:27.000Z","msg":"現年23歲的王卓雅為全職社區主任，她表示過往曾多次受到電話騷擾，包括在電話中表達露骨字眼，惟今次是首度在進行地區工作期間，有人以身體接觸形式非禮，她認為事態嚴重，不能啞忍，因此報警。王又表示，「女仔落區困難會較多」，例如較容易被抹黑，「<span style=\"color: red;\">有人會話你做雞，或者話你性生活好亂」</span>，不過她表示不會被此類騷擾乃至非禮嚇怕，會繼續在區內服務街坊，就算再遇到事件亦會挺身而出舉報，絕不姑息，「佢對得你做，可能下次就會對你啲街坊咁做。」"},{"pid":"af2abb446ca118553cda7a65a6eafcd107ca4c1b","tid":1032494,"uid":163082,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"856f727ad4fb36aecfef53508bcf6147e31a500e","tid":1032494,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2471575/org/92513f4aa468c2348f8fee9eb4065afc.jpg/97fg-K-YCYd73QeS6gPzIvbNYcWHTX9e1kA3zdZAN80?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2471575%2Forg%2F92513f4aa468c2348f8fee9eb4065afc.jpg%2F97fg-K-YCYd73QeS6gPzIvbNYcWHTX9e1kA3zdZAN80%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2ae40475&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"位男士好似發現啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145f967d04eb7c9df3e31445599a4d2043e71b3e","tid":1032494,"uid":19454,"like":0,"